09:18.350 --> 09:20.101
<i>"Wait, doesn't Jane</i>

09:18.350 --> 09:20.101
<i>like Dennis just fine?"</i>

09:20.101 --> 09:21.895
<i>Well, the answer is no,</i>

09:20.101 --> 09:21.895
<i>but I don't have time</i>

09:21.895 --> 09:23.480
<i>to explain now. Just trust me.</i>

09:21.895 --> 09:23.480
MAN: Jane?

09:23.480 --> 09:25.357
<i>She hasn't had</i>

09:23.480 --> 09:25.357
<i>a panic attack in forever.</i>

09:25.357 --> 09:27.025
Jane?

09:25.357 --> 09:27.025
<i>Remember your coping</i>

09:27.025 --> 09:29.277
<i>mechanisms, Jane.</i>

09:27.025 --> 09:29.277
( panting )

09:36.535 --> 09:38.995
Jane?

09:36.535 --> 09:38.995
( grunts )

09:38.995 --> 09:41.998
NARRATOR:

09:38.995 --> 09:41.998
<i>Wow. Even I didn't</i>

09:38.995 --> 09:41.998
<i>see that coming.</i>

09:45.168 --> 09:48.505
Oh, my God. I'm so...

09:45.168 --> 09:48.505
No, um...

09:48.505 --> 09:51.216
I-It's okay.

09:48.505 --> 09:51.216
But you deserved it. So sorry.

09:51.216 --> 09:53.301
Look, can we talk?

09:51.216 --> 09:53.301
No.

09:53.301 --> 09:54.553
Jane, we--

09:53.301 --> 09:54.553
I don't want

09:54.553 --> 09:57.180
to talk to you<i> ever.</i>

09:58.473 --> 10:00.016
( panting )

10:06.814 --> 10:10.151
I still can't believe it.

10:10.151 --> 10:13.238
( sniffles ):

10:10.151 --> 10:13.238
I know.

10:16.116 --> 10:17.367
( crying )

10:17.367 --> 10:19.578
I'm gonna check up on you, okay?

10:19.578 --> 10:21.121
( sniffles )

10:21.121 --> 10:22.622
ALBA ( in Spanish ):

10:21.121 --> 10:22.622
<i>You slapped him?</i>

10:22.622 --> 10:25.708
( in English ):

10:22.622 --> 10:25.708
I know. It's just...

10:25.708 --> 10:28.545
Ah. I started

10:25.708 --> 10:28.545
having a panic attack.

10:28.545 --> 10:29.796
( in Spanish ):

10:28.545 --> 10:29.796
Ah. You did?

10:29.796 --> 10:33.174
But you haven't had one

10:29.796 --> 10:33.174
in so long.

10:33.174 --> 10:35.594
( in English ):

10:33.174 --> 10:35.594
I was thrown. I wasn't

10:33.174 --> 10:35.594
expecting to see him.

10:35.594 --> 10:37.512
( in Spanish ):

10:35.594 --> 10:37.512
Why was he there?

10:37.512 --> 10:40.181
( in English ):

10:37.512 --> 10:40.181
Apparently, he's running

10:37.512 --> 10:40.181
the Scott investigation

10:40.181 --> 10:42.225
at the hotel, so he has to

10:40.181 --> 10:42.225
interview all the employees,

10:42.225 --> 10:43.768
including you<i> and</i> me.

10:43.768 --> 10:45.353
( in Spanish ):

10:43.768 --> 10:45.353
Want me to slap him?

10:45.353 --> 10:47.481
( in English) :

10:45.353 --> 10:47.481
I'll be fine.

10:47.481 --> 10:50.275
I just wasn't prepared.

10:47.481 --> 10:50.275
Now I'm prepared.

10:50.275 --> 10:53.528
No.A salad lead time of

10:50.275 --> 10:53.528
11 minutes is unacceptable.

10:53.528 --> 10:56.323
All salads and cold apps need

10:53.528 --> 10:56.323
to be delivered to the table

10:56.323 --> 10:58.241
within six minutes

10:56.323 --> 10:58.241
of the order being placed.

10:58.241 --> 10:59.659
I understand. I'm sorry.

10:59.659 --> 11:02.245
It won't happen again.

11:02.245 --> 11:04.414
Hey, yesterday

11:02.245 --> 11:04.414
it was 15 minutes.

11:04.414 --> 11:06.124
So he's improving.

11:06.124 --> 11:09.710
I am getting so tired

11:06.124 --> 11:09.710
of Zen Rafael.

11:09.710 --> 11:11.796
You hired him, you fire him.

11:11.796 --> 11:13.548
( phone chimes )

11:15.800 --> 11:17.552
Oh, no.

11:18.761 --> 11:20.221
Someone leaked the story.

11:20.221 --> 11:21.348
I hate to say I told you so.

11:21.348 --> 11:22.723
NARRATOR:

11:21.348 --> 11:22.723
<i>And yet...</i>

11:22.723 --> 11:24.225
We should've gotten

11:22.723 --> 11:24.225
ahead of it.

11:24.225 --> 11:26.894
All it takes is

11:24.225 --> 11:26.894
one disgruntled employee.

11:26.894 --> 11:30.190
( whispers ):

11:26.894 --> 11:30.190
And trust me,

11:26.894 --> 11:30.190
we have more than one.

11:31.483 --> 11:32.984
SONIA:

11:31.483 --> 11:32.984
So, so sorry

11:32.984 --> 11:34.902
for the wait.

11:36.279 --> 11:38.406
Great. You told me so.

11:36.279 --> 11:38.406
That's not important.

11:38.406 --> 11:40.158
What do we do now?

11:42.494 --> 11:45.455
I know this doesn't

11:42.494 --> 11:45.455
undo what I did,

11:45.455 --> 11:48.416
