11:45.455 --> 11:48.416
my apologies.

11:48.416 --> 11:51.044
I had my assistant go

11:48.416 --> 11:51.044
nuts at the bookstore.

11:51.044 --> 11:52.795
There are books

11:51.044 --> 11:52.795
about writing books,

11:52.795 --> 11:54.172
books about

11:52.795 --> 11:54.172
reading books--

11:54.172 --> 11:56.383
Dad, I appreciate

11:54.172 --> 11:56.383
all the books, but--

11:56.383 --> 11:57.592
Even books about forgiving.

11:57.592 --> 11:59.511
"Forgiveness

11:57.592 --> 11:59.511
is a gift

11:59.511 --> 12:01.095
you give yourself."

12:01.095 --> 12:02.930
Deepak Chopra.

12:02.930 --> 12:05.099
Via Suzanne Somers.

12:05.099 --> 12:07.060
Look, I know

12:05.099 --> 12:07.060
that you're sorry, but--

12:07.060 --> 12:08.687
I never meant

12:07.060 --> 12:08.687
to hurt anyone.

12:08.687 --> 12:10.188
But you did.

12:10.188 --> 12:12.399
And it's gonna take a while

12:10.188 --> 12:12.399
for people to forgive you

12:12.399 --> 12:13.900
no matter

12:12.399 --> 12:13.900
how many books you buy.

12:13.900 --> 12:15.276
I understand.

12:15.276 --> 12:17.945
I'm just trying

12:15.276 --> 12:17.945
to get the process started.

12:17.945 --> 12:20.532
Because I love you, Jane.

12:17.945 --> 12:20.532
You know that.

12:20.532 --> 12:22.992
And I love you, too.

12:25.119 --> 12:28.081
But I-I don't think

12:25.119 --> 12:28.081
Mom's gonna get past this.

12:28.081 --> 12:31.543
Her Ropology basket

12:28.081 --> 12:31.543
is a work of art.

12:31.543 --> 12:33.002
( phone chimes )

12:33.002 --> 12:34.921
Oh, my God. It's my offer

12:33.002 --> 12:34.921
from the publisher.

12:34.921 --> 12:36.506
NARRATOR:

12:34.921 --> 12:36.506
<i>I'm so excited!</i>

12:36.506 --> 12:38.383
<i>Let's see how much money</i>

12:36.506 --> 12:38.383
<i>Jane's going to get.</i>

12:38.383 --> 12:39.676
( shrieks )

12:39.676 --> 12:43.054
I am getting $50,000!

12:43.054 --> 12:44.472
What? That's it?

12:44.472 --> 12:47.058
( chuckles ):

12:44.472 --> 12:47.058
That's barely my episodic rate.

12:48.560 --> 12:51.312
No, that's amazing.

12:48.560 --> 12:51.312
$50,000 is a lot of money.

12:51.312 --> 12:53.231
It's a huge amount of money.

12:51.312 --> 12:53.231
What was I thinking?

12:53.231 --> 12:54.815
Let me get that scene

12:53.231 --> 12:54.815
from the top.

12:56.192 --> 12:58.945
$50,000, Jane! Holy moly!

12:58.945 --> 13:00.739
Congratulations!

13:00.739 --> 13:02.198
Oh. Ha.

13:02.198 --> 13:04.117
It's a year's salary.

13:04.117 --> 13:07.328
So I can finally give

13:04.117 --> 13:07.328
my two-week notice to Chloe.

13:07.328 --> 13:09.414
NARRATOR:

13:07.328 --> 13:09.414
<i>Oh, yeah.</i>

13:09.414 --> 13:11.458
<i>Someone's got</i>

13:09.414 --> 13:11.458
<i>her quittin' heels on.</i>

13:17.589 --> 13:20.341
I have had it with Chloe

13:17.589 --> 13:20.341
and her ridiculous notes.

13:20.341 --> 13:22.260
I am not a hack, Jane!

13:22.260 --> 13:24.387
No one said you are, Gary.

13:22.260 --> 13:24.387
You know Chloe.

13:24.387 --> 13:26.514
You just got to breathe

13:24.387 --> 13:26.514
through it.

13:26.514 --> 13:29.142
( inhales, exhales ):

13:26.514 --> 13:29.142
Ah...

13:29.142 --> 13:32.312
We'll talk later, okay?

13:32.312 --> 13:35.231
NARRATOR:

13:32.312 --> 13:35.231
<i>Or hashtag</i>

13:32.312 --> 13:35.231
<i>"someone else's problem."</i>

13:37.150 --> 13:39.694
So, I have some exciting news.

13:39.694 --> 13:41.362
After the writers'

13:39.694 --> 13:41.362
showcase,

13:41.362 --> 13:43.364
I was actually offered

13:41.362 --> 13:43.364
a book deal.

13:43.364 --> 13:44.699
And?

13:45.659 --> 13:46.951
And...

13:46.951 --> 13:48.453
yay!

13:51.581 --> 13:54.083
So I'm giving

13:51.581 --> 13:54.083
my two-week notice.

13:56.169 --> 13:59.880
And I wanted to say thank you

13:56.169 --> 13:59.880
for the wonderful opportunity.

13:59.880 --> 14:02.008
It was amazing.

14:03.968 --> 14:07.263
So thank you.

14:07.263 --> 14:10.517
Very, very, very much.

14:10.517 --> 14:11.768
No.

14:11.768 --> 14:13.728
Two weeks' notice

14:11.768 --> 14:13.728
is unacceptable.

14:13.728 --> 14:16.022
I need at least six months,

14:13.728 --> 14:16.022
preferably a year,

14:16.022 --> 14:17.856
to find and train

14:16.022 --> 14:17.856
a new assistant.

14:17.856 --> 14:19.818
( stammers )

14:19.818 --> 14:22.654
T-Two weeks' notice is

14:19.818 --> 14:22.654
pretty much industry standard.

14:22.654 --> 14:25.448
Now you're lecturing me

14:22.654 --> 14:25.448
on industry standard?

14:25.448 --> 14:26.658
No. God, never. No.

14:26.658 --> 14:28.909
Uh... I could stay

14:26.658 --> 14:28.909
a little longer.

14:28.909 --> 14:31.078
( groans ):

14:28.909 --> 14:31.078
Oh, please.

14:31.078 --> 14:33.456
Go. You were terrible

14:31.078 --> 14:33.456
at your job.

14:33.456 --> 14:34.666
What?

14:34.666 --> 14:36.167
And you're

14:34.666 --> 14:36.167
deluding yourself

14:36.167 --> 14:38.044
if you think this book

14:36.167 --> 14:38.044
deal's going anywhere,

14:38.044 --> 14:40.714
especially with that

14:38.044 --> 14:40.714
ridiculous D-list publisher.

14:40.714 --> 14:43.174
But congrats, you're

14:40.714 --> 14:43.174
a half a step above

14:43.174 --> 14:44.509
self-publishing online.

14:46.761 --> 14:48.262
Wow.

14:48.262 --> 14:50.097
Chloe...

14:50.097 --> 14:52.141
you're a horrible person.

14:52.141 --> 14:54.310
And I tried

14:54.310 --> 14:56.521
to make excuses for you

14:54.310 --> 14:56.521
over the years,

14:56.521 --> 14:58.314
like maybe your parents

14:56.521 --> 14:58.314
didn't hug you,

14:58.314 --> 15:00.650
or maybe you grew up

14:58.314 --> 15:00.650
in a prison like Bane

15:00.650 --> 15:02.527
from that Batman movie,

15:00.650 --> 15:02.527
but I just think

15:02.527 --> 15:06.656
it comes down to who you are:

15:02.527 --> 15:06.656
a petty, mean-spirited bitch!

15:06.656 --> 15:08.115
NARRATOR:

15:06.656 --> 15:08.115
<i>Atta girl, Jane.</i>

15:08.115 --> 15:09.659
<i>I'm proud of you.</i>

15:09.659 --> 15:11.536
<i>She deserved that.</i>

15:11.536 --> 15:14.121
God knows

15:11.536 --> 15:14.121
Scott did not deserve this.

15:14.121 --> 15:16.499
And I am so sad about this.

15:16.499 --> 15:18.042
( sobs softly )

15:18.042 --> 15:20.211
Which is why...

15:20.211 --> 15:22.213
we're dedicating

15:20.211 --> 15:22.213
this fountain to him,

15:22.213 --> 15:24.173
and creating a scholarship fund

15:22.213 --> 15:24.173
in his name

15:24.173 --> 15:25.341
for disadvantaged youth.

15:25.341 --> 15:26.885
( sighs ):

15:25.341 --> 15:26.885
And even though

15:26.885 --> 15:30.388
he died next-door,

15:26.885 --> 15:30.388
and not here at

15:30.388 --> 15:32.515
his beloved Marbella,

15:32.515 --> 15:35.393
his tragic loss will reverberate

15:32.515 --> 15:35.393
through these halls

15:35.393 --> 15:37.270
for years to come.

15:39.480 --> 15:42.400
Farewell, my friend.

15:42.400 --> 15:43.651
Farewell.

15:43.651 --> 15:45.027
( applause )

15:49.282 --> 15:50.533
Just know I feel terrible.

15:50.533 --> 15:51.910
VAN:

15:50.533 --> 15:51.910
<i>You should.</i>

15:51.910 --> 15:53.745
It's like North Korea here.

15:53.745 --> 15:55.705
Everyone's scared to say

15:53.745 --> 15:55.705
anything to Kim Jong-Chloe.

15:55.705 --> 15:57.457
<i>She told me to figure out</i>

15:55.705 --> 15:57.457
<i>everything you knew</i>

15:57.457 --> 15:58.999
<i>but not to call you.</i>

15:58.999 --> 16:00.877
If I get caught--

15:58.999 --> 16:00.877
<i>Don't worry, it sounds like she</i>

16:00.877 --> 16:02.462
wants you to call me

16:00.877 --> 16:02.462
but doesn't want you

16:02.462 --> 16:03.838
to know

16:02.462 --> 16:03.838
she wants you to call me.

16:03.838 --> 16:05.590
You're fine. And you've got...

16:05.590 --> 16:07.634
15 more minutes before

16:05.590 --> 16:07.634
she gets back from therapy,

16:07.634 --> 16:09.135
so hit me up.

16:09.135 --> 16:10.470
Sweat and Spin password?

16:10.470 --> 16:12.263
Zero-three-ten.

16:10.470 --> 16:12.263
BlowoutHeaven stylist?

16:12.263 --> 16:13.598
Lana for Beachy Waves,

16:13.598 --> 16:14.891
Quentin if she wants

16:13.598 --> 16:14.891
a Straight-Up,

16:14.891 --> 16:16.476
<i>and always</i>

16:14.891 --> 16:16.476
<i>with a scalp massage.</i>

16:16.476 --> 16:18.311
<i>Always</i> with a scalp massage.

16:16.476 --> 16:18.311
VAN: Got it.

16:18.311 --> 16:19.854
Coffee order?

16:18.311 --> 16:19.854
JANE: For a cold brew,

16:19.854 --> 16:21.355
Davey's 20-ounce Baridi Blend.

16:21.355 --> 16:22.816
For tea, InstaJava Venti

16:22.816 --> 16:24.484
<i>Iced Green Latte.</i>

16:22.816 --> 16:24.484
<i>And don't leave there</i>

16:24.484 --> 16:26.402
