31:09.201 --> 31:12.204
it really does a great job

31:09.201 --> 31:12.204
of masking that empty feeling.

31:15.415 --> 31:18.251
Well, I'm done, Darci.

31:18.251 --> 31:21.380
You can't quit.

31:18.251 --> 31:21.380
