31:26.760 --> 31:29.471
What's Papa apologizing

31:26.760 --> 31:29.471
to me for?

31:29.471 --> 31:30.723
Don't worry about it.

31:30.723 --> 31:34.017
Just take the gift

31:30.723 --> 31:34.017
and say thank you.

