Can we color a little?

31:36.228 --> 31:37.563
One page, then bedtime.

31:46.613 --> 31:48.448
( panting softly )

31:50.950 --> 31:53.579
A...giraffe.

31:53.579 --> 31:55.288
( echoing ):

31:53.579 --> 31:55.288
Mommy, are you okay?

31:55.288 --> 31:56.707
( gasping )

31:56.707 --> 31:58.917
Mommy? Mommy?

32:00.627 --> 32:01.961
Oh.

32:01.961 --> 32:04.464
Mommy?

32:01.961 --> 32:04.464
Sorry, hon.

32:04.464 --> 32:07.259
You had that face.

32:04.464 --> 32:07.259
Were you thinking about Michael?

32:09.469 --> 32:11.179
A little, yeah.

32:11.179 --> 32:12.514
How come now?

32:12.514 --> 32:15.267
Well, I saw someone

32:12.514 --> 32:15.267
that was mean to him,

32:15.267 --> 32:16.727
and it made me mad.

32:16.727 --> 32:18.978
Did you use your words?

32:21.690 --> 32:24.359
You know, I really didn't.

32:24.359 --> 32:26.403
You should.

32:26.403 --> 32:28.154
You're right.

32:28.154 --> 32:29.615
I will.

32:29.615 --> 32:31.533
Oh, you.

32:31.533 --> 32:32.826
( sniffles )

32:41.418 --> 32:44.838
Okay. Mommy asked him to talk.

32:46.047 --> 32:47.382
( phone chimes )

32:52.220 --> 32:56.141
NARRATOR:

32:52.220 --> 32:56.141
<i>Which brings us here...now.</i>

32:56.141 --> 32:59.311
<i>I know. I was expecting,</i>

32:56.141 --> 32:59.311
<i>like, a cafe or something.</i>

33:01.062 --> 33:02.439
Why are we here?

33:02.439 --> 33:04.065
I figure if you're gonna

33:02.439 --> 33:04.065
keep hitting me,

33:04.065 --> 33:05.901
at least you can

33:04.065 --> 33:05.901
wear gloves.

33:05.901 --> 33:08.612
Look, I just want to talk.

33:05.901 --> 33:08.612
I'm not gonna hit you again.

33:08.612 --> 33:12.240
Fine. I just want to explain

33:08.612 --> 33:12.240
my side of the story.

33:12.240 --> 33:13.533
When Michael passed away,

33:13.533 --> 33:15.285
I joined the department's

33:13.533 --> 33:15.285
investigation to--

33:15.285 --> 33:16.870
No, you're right.

33:15.285 --> 33:16.870
I do want to hit you.

33:16.870 --> 33:18.204
Give me those gloves.

33:22.459 --> 33:25.545
Don't forget to practice.

33:27.673 --> 33:29.842
I don't want to talk to you.

33:27.673 --> 33:29.842
I know. I know.

33:29.842 --> 33:31.343
I just wanted

33:29.842 --> 33:31.343
to tell you,

33:31.343 --> 33:32.803
I've been doing

33:31.343 --> 33:32.803
some soul searching,

33:32.803 --> 33:34.930
and I realize

33:32.803 --> 33:34.930
I've lost my way.

33:34.930 --> 33:36.723
Yeah. No kidding.

33:36.723 --> 33:40.101
I just want to go back to

33:36.723 --> 33:40.101
how things were before I became

33:40.101 --> 33:42.145
this crazy famous

33:40.101 --> 33:42.145
reality TV star,

33:42.145 --> 33:44.564
when I was just a simple

33:42.145 --> 33:44.564
internationally famous

33:44.564 --> 33:46.608
telenovela star.

33:46.608 --> 33:49.235
And I'm gonna try

33:46.608 --> 33:49.235
to get back to that guy.

33:49.235 --> 33:51.404
And he was honest.

33:51.404 --> 33:54.240
And if I'm honest,

33:54.240 --> 33:58.244
I think I agreed to the cut

33:54.240 --> 33:58.244
because I was jealous.

33:58.244 --> 34:01.289
You had just

33:58.244 --> 34:01.289
moved in with Bruce,

34:01.289 --> 34:04.626
and I think

34:01.289 --> 34:04.626
I wanted to hurt you.

34:07.045 --> 34:09.798
And I'm so sorry.

34:11.967 --> 34:15.428
NARRATOR:

34:11.967 --> 34:15.428
<i>And from one troubled</i>

34:11.967 --> 34:15.428
<i>friendship to another.</i>

34:15.428 --> 34:17.973
<i>Oh, wow! Look at Jane!</i>

34:17.973 --> 34:19.975
<i>She's pummeling him!</i>

34:22.143 --> 34:23.687
<i>In her mind.</i>

34:22.143 --> 34:23.687
( bell dings )

34:23.687 --> 34:25.230
<i>In reality...</i>

34:25.230 --> 34:27.649
You are such a jerk!

34:27.649 --> 34:28.901
I'm so mad at you.

34:28.901 --> 34:30.109
Whoa.

34:30.109 --> 34:31.737
No kicking.

34:30.109 --> 34:31.737
Sorry.

34:31.737 --> 34:33.321
