I didn't use you.

34:40.119 --> 34:41.329
You did!

34:41.329 --> 34:42.664
I trusted you,

34:42.664 --> 34:44.416
and you went through

34:42.664 --> 34:44.416
Michael's stuff!

34:44.416 --> 34:47.711
I had to.

34:44.416 --> 34:47.711
What-- you had to spy on him?

34:47.711 --> 34:49.170
I was trying to clear his name.

34:49.170 --> 34:51.297
The whole time, I was

34:49.170 --> 34:51.297
trying to clear his name.

34:51.297 --> 34:53.091
I don't believe that.

34:51.297 --> 34:53.091
It's true.

34:53.091 --> 34:55.260
There was an investigation.

34:53.091 --> 34:55.260
You didn't have to work it.

34:55.260 --> 34:56.845
Would you want

34:55.260 --> 34:56.845
someone else to?

34:56.845 --> 34:59.056
