34:56.845 --> 34:59.056
I was trying to protect you.

34:59.056 --> 35:01.307
I don't need protecting!

35:01.307 --> 35:03.226
Not now, but then.

35:03.226 --> 35:05.395
You were having panic

35:03.226 --> 35:05.395
attacks every day!

35:05.395 --> 35:06.813
( bell dings )

35:05.395 --> 35:06.813
( grunts )

35:13.695 --> 35:15.572
I'm sorry, again.

35:15.572 --> 35:18.408
Not your fault.

35:18.408 --> 35:20.326
( sighs )

35:20.326 --> 35:21.620
You're right.

35:23.663 --> 35:26.959
I was in

35:23.663 --> 35:26.959
