35:26.959 --> 35:29.544
( sighs )

35:29.544 --> 35:32.171
It just sucked,

35:29.544 --> 35:32.171
because you were the one person

35:32.171 --> 35:34.173
that I could talk to

35:32.171 --> 35:34.173
or could--

35:34.173 --> 35:37.385
I don't know--

35:34.173 --> 35:37.385
tell me new things

35:37.385 --> 35:40.639
about Michael,

35:37.385 --> 35:40.639
things I didn't know.

35:40.639 --> 35:44.142
Hearing that he was

35:40.639 --> 35:44.142
a ball hog, or...

35:46.103 --> 35:49.439
