35:46.103 --> 35:49.439
our first date or whatever.

35:51.149 --> 35:54.569
It just kept him alive a little.

35:54.569 --> 35:56.154
I know.

35:57.990 --> 36:00.033
Well, I'm here

35:57.990 --> 36:00.033
every Tuesday,

36:00.033 --> 36:01.868
if you ever get

36:00.033 --> 36:01.868
the urge to talk,

36:01.868 --> 36:04.955
or, you know,

36:01.868 --> 36:04.955
hit me again.

