36:15.381 --> 36:18.802
Really? 'Cause I had a list of,

36:15.381 --> 36:18.802
like, 50 suspects in mind.

36:21.805 --> 36:24.223
Yep. The Marbella is totally

36:21.805 --> 36:24.223
off the hook.

36:24.223 --> 36:25.391
The Fairwick, too.

36:25.391 --> 36:27.060
JANE:

36:25.391 --> 36:27.060
<i>That's great.</i>

36:27.060 --> 36:28.603
I'm so happy for you.

