37:12.939 --> 37:15.734
<i>And if it doesn't</i>

37:12.939 --> 37:15.734
<i>happen for me,</i>

37:15.734 --> 37:17.443
then I'd be a lounge manager,

37:17.443 --> 37:19.946
as opposed to someone working

37:17.443 --> 37:19.946
in the publishing industry.

37:19.946 --> 37:21.781
You're talking about

37:19.946 --> 37:21.781
if you fail.

37:21.781 --> 37:23.533
I'm being practical.

37:23.533 --> 37:25.451
What happened

37:23.533 --> 37:25.451
to following your dreams?

37:26.912 --> 37:29.581
Well, y-you know, I...

37:29.581 --> 37:31.208
I had a dream.

37:31.208 --> 37:34.127
(<i> romantic theme playing</i> )

37:34.127 --> 37:36.171
RAFAEL:

37:34.127 --> 37:36.171
<i>I know.</i>

37:36.171 --> 37:37.756
But you do have other ones.

37:37.756 --> 37:40.217
<i>And I won't let you get stuck</i>

37:37.756 --> 37:40.217
<i>in the lounge.</i>

37:40.217 --> 37:41.927
Okay?

37:41.927 --> 37:43.469
Two years and you're out.

37:43.469 --> 37:45.013
Promise?

37:45.013 --> 37:46.890
Promise.

37:46.890 --> 37:50.185
Because you'd want me

37:46.890 --> 37:50.185
to tell you if you were stuck.

37:50.185 --> 37:52.145
Exactly.

37:52.145 --> 37:53.563
You're stuck.

37:53.563 --> 37:55.607
<i>At work, you're basically</i>

37:53.563 --> 37:55.607
<i>Petra's bitch.</i>

37:55.607 --> 37:57.275
<i>And I say that</i>

37:55.607 --> 37:57.275
<i>with full respect</i>

37:57.275 --> 37:58.651
for Petra.

37:58.651 --> 38:00.361
You're not gonna turn back

37:58.651 --> 38:00.361
into greedy,

38:00.361 --> 38:02.030
shady, amoral Rafael

38:02.030 --> 38:04.157
just because you care about

38:02.030 --> 38:04.157
the Marbella.

38:04.157 --> 38:07.619
Greedy, shady, amoral Rafael?

38:07.619 --> 38:10.329
Paraphrasing.

38:07.619 --> 38:10.329
Just think about it.

38:10.329 --> 38:13.833
NARRATOR:

38:10.329 --> 38:13.833
<i>Which he did, for the record.</i>

38:13.833 --> 38:16.711
So just like that?

38:16.711 --> 38:19.714
After a year of "you decide,"

38:16.711 --> 38:19.714
