38:19.714 --> 38:22.759
Yes. I'm ready.

38:22.759 --> 38:25.428
Well, it's about time.

38:25.428 --> 38:27.639
ABBEY: See?

38:25.428 --> 38:27.639
I knew she'd be happy.

38:27.639 --> 38:29.390
NARRATOR:

38:27.639 --> 38:29.390
<i>Oh, God. Sorry, again.</i>

38:29.390 --> 38:31.726
<i>So embarrassing.</i>

38:29.390 --> 38:31.726
<i>I should look into this.</i>

38:31.726 --> 38:33.686
Well, he actually has

38:31.726 --> 38:33.686
