38:33.686 --> 38:35.730
Wow. High praise.

38:35.730 --> 38:37.107
But he has to lose

38:35.730 --> 38:37.107
the beard, right?

38:37.107 --> 38:38.399
Oh, absolutely.

38:38.399 --> 38:39.651
Yeah.

38:39.651 --> 38:41.236
It's a prerequisite.

38:41.236 --> 38:43.905
I'm going back

38:41.236 --> 38:43.905
to telenovelas, Mateo.

38:43.905 --> 38:47.117
You are too young to remember,

38:43.905 --> 38:47.117
but Papa played some epic roles.

38:47.117 --> 38:50.078
So my next role

38:47.117 --> 38:50.078
